snippet.title: Deathground Pre-Alpha Reveal Trailer | Dinosaur Survival Horror Game | 2020
snippet.description:
All content shown is Pre-Alpha.
If you like the look of the game, please consider backing on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/jawdropgames/deathground

Deathground is a solo and co-op survival horror game that throws players into a desperate battle for survival against deadly AI dinosaurs.

Deathground features solo and squad-based action, reactive AI dinosaurs, special character classes, truly terrifying environments and intense and replayable gameplay. 

------------------------------------

We are currently running a Kickstarter campaign so if you would like to pledge your support and join this journey with us, follow the link below. Every backer counts!

Pledge on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/jawdropgames/deathground
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1200770/Deathground
More information: https://deathgroundgame.com/

Social
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/deathgroundgame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/deathground_game
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/deathgroundgame

#Dinosaurs #Survival #Horror #Kickstarter
